Description: This field is used to record the association of the documented actor to a national body, usually indicating its legal or citizenship association.
This field is used to record founding members of the documented group.
This field is used to record a member of the documented group.
This field is used to record the type of role the member played in relation to the documented group.
This field is used to indicate the earliest possible date of becoming a member of the documented group by the referenced person.
This field is used to indicate the latest possible date of becoming a member of the documented group by the referenced person.
This field is used to record the earliest possible date of ceasing to be a member of the documented group by the referenced person.
This field is used to record the latest possible date of ceasing to be a member of the documented group by the referenced person.
